      • setParentTraceId

        public final void setParentTraceId(java.lang.Thread t,
                                   long traceId,
                                   int orderId)
        Sets the parent for the next created trace inside this thread. This method should be used by probes in connection with SpliEvents.
        Parameters:
        t - the thread the new trace belongs to
        traceId - the parent trace id
        orderId - the parent order id
